query:
SELECT cc.componentName, cc.componentType, cc.allowableStress, cc.jointEfficiency, cc.actualThickness, cc.minimumThickness, cc.timeSpan, i.vesselTagNumber 
FROM componentCalculations cc 
JOIN professionalReports pr ON cc.reportId = pr.id 
JOIN inspections i ON pr.inspectionId = i.id 
WHERE i.vesselTagNumber LIKE '%54-11-005%' 
ORDER BY cc.componentName LIMIT 10
